('Ocean Master Diver Pro', 'ocean-master-diver-pro', 'Built for the depths, the Ocean Master Diver Pro is the ultimate tool watch for serious divers. Featuring a helium escape valve, unidirectional rotating bezel, and luminous markers for perfect legibility in the darkest waters. A true companion for underwater adventures.', '{"Movement": "Automatic", "Case Material": "Titanium", "Crystal": "Sapphire", "Water Resistance": "500m", "Strap": "Rubber", "Diameter": "44mm", "Bezel": "Ceramic Unidirectional", "Lume": "Super-LumiNova"}', 3200000, null, 8, 'Diver', 'Ocean Master', true, false, true, ARRAY['https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1524592094714-0f0654e20314?w=800', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1539874754764-5a96559165b0?w=800']),

('Heritage Classic Gold', 'heritage-classic-gold', 'The Heritage Classic Gold pays homage to timeless design with its elegant gold-plated case and minimalist dial. Roman numeral indices and blued steel hands create a sophisticated aesthetic that transcends trends. The perfect dress watch for formal occasions.', '{"Movement": "Quartz", "Case Material": "Gold-Plated Stainless Steel", "Crystal": "Mineral", "Water Resistance": "30m", "Strap": "Crocodile Leather", "Diameter": "38mm", "Thickness": "8mm", "Battery Life": "3 years"}', 1850000, 1650000, 22, 'Dress', 'Heritage', true, true, false, ARRAY['https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1547996663-b0f255ffb89d?w=800', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507679799987-c73729787bd1?w=800']),

('Aviator Pilot GMT', 'aviator-pilot-gmt', 'Designed for the modern traveler, the Aviator Pilot GMT features a dual-time zone display and a 24-hour bezel. The brushed steel case and anti-reflective sapphire crystal ensure durability and clarity. A reliable companion for pilots and globetrotters alike.', '{"Movement": "Automatic GMT", "Case Material": "Brushed Steel", "Crystal": "AR Sapphire", "Water Resistance": "100m", "Strap": "Stainless Steel Bracelet", "Diameter": "40mm", "GMT Hand": "24-hour", "Crown": "Screw-down"}', 2450000, null, 12, 'Pilot', 'Aviator', false, true, false, ARRAY['https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523170335258-f5ed11844a49?w=800', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1612817159949-195b6eb9e31a?w=800']),

('Summit Explorer Titanium', 'summit-explorer-titanium', 'Forged from aerospace-grade titanium, the Summit Explorer is built for extreme conditions. The altimeter, barometer, and compass functions make it indispensable for mountaineers. Despite its rugged capabilities, it maintains an elegant profile suitable for everyday wear.', '{"Movement": "Solar Quartz", "Case Material": "Grade 5 Titanium", "Crystal": "Sapphire", "Water Resistance": "100m", "Strap": "Titanium Bracelet", "Diameter": "43mm", "Sensors": "Altimeter, Barometer, Compass", "Weight": "98g"}', 4100000, 3750000, 6, 'Field', 'Summit', true, false, true, ARRAY['https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1522312346375-d1a52e2b99b3?w=800', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1524592094714-0f0654e20314?w=800']),

('Elegance Rose Gold', 'elegance-rose-gold', 'The Elegance Rose Gold captures feminine sophistication with its rose gold case and mother-of-pearl dial. Diamond hour markers add a touch of luxury, while the slim profile ensures it sits gracefully on the wrist. A statement piece for the modern woman.', '{"Movement": "Automatic", "Case Material": "18K Rose Gold Plated", "Crystal": "Sapphire", "Water Resistance": "50m", "Strap": "Satin", "Diameter": "34mm", "Thickness": "9mm", "Dial": "Mother of Pearl"}', 2100000, 1890000, 18, 'Dress', 'Elegance', false, true, false, ARRAY['https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507679799987-c73729787bd1?w=800', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1547996663-b0f255ffb89d?w=800']),

('Speed Racer Chronograph', 'speed-racer-chronograph', 'Inspired by motorsport, the Speed Racer Chronograph features a tachymeter scale and split-second timing. The carbon fiber dial and perforated leather strap evoke the spirit of the racetrack. Precision engineering meets adrenaline-fueled design.', '{"Movement": "Automatic Chronograph", "Case Material": "Carbon Fiber & Steel", "Crystal": "Sapphire", "Water Resistance": "100m", "Strap": "Perforated Leather", "Diameter": "41mm", "Functions": "Tachymeter, Split-seconds", "Pushers": "Screw-down"}', 2950000, null, 10, 'Chronograph', 'Speed Racer', false, false, true, ARRAY['https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1539874754764-5a96559165b0?w=800', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523170335258-f5ed11844a49?w=800']),

('Navy Admiral Automatic', 'navy-admiral-automatic', 'Paying tribute to naval heritage, the Navy Admiral features a deep blue dial with gold accents and a nautical-inspired bezel. The exhibition caseback reveals the decorated automatic movement. A watch that commands respect on land and sea.', '{"Movement": "Automatic", "Case Material": "Polished Steel", "Crystal": "Sapphire", "Water Resistance": "200m", "Strap": "Navy Canvas", "Diameter": "42mm", "Caseback": "Exhibition", "Bezel": "Nautical 60-minute"}', 2250000, 1990000, 14, 'Diver', 'Navy Admiral', false, true, false, ARRAY['https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1612817159949-195b6eb9e31a?w=800', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1524592094714-0f0654e20314?w=800']),

('Vintage 1960 Reissue', 'vintage-1960-reissue', 'A faithful recreation of a 1960s classic, the Vintage Reissue captures the charm of a bygone era. The domed acrylic crystal, patina-inspired lume, and hand-wound movement offer an authentic vintage experience. For collectors who appreciate horological history.', '{"Movement": "Hand-wound", "Case Material": "Stainless Steel", "Crystal": "Domed Acrylic", "Water Resistance": "30m", "Strap": "Vintage Leather", "Diameter": "36mm", "Lume": "Patina-style", "Crown": "Onion-style"}', 1650000, null, 20, 'Dress', 'Vintage', false, false, true, ARRAY['https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1547996663-b0f255ffb89d?w=800', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507679799987-c73729787bd1?w=800']),

('Stealth Tactical Black', 'stealth-tactical-black', 'The Stealth Tactical is engineered for covert operations with its all-black PVD coating and subdued dial. The tritium tubes provide constant illumination without charging. Built to military specifications, this watch is as tough as it is discreet.', '{"Movement": "Automatic", "Case Material": "PVD Coated Steel", "Crystal": "Sapphire", "Water Resistance": "300m", "Strap": "Black NATO", "Diameter": "42mm", "Lume": "Tritium Tubes", "Coating": "Diamond-like Carbon"}', 2750000, 2490000, 9, 'Field', 'Stealth', false, true, false, ARRAY['https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1523170335258-f5ed11844a49?w=800', 'https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1539874754764-5a96559165b0?w=800']);



